headline: Colgate-Palmolive Webcasts Fireside Chat at the Goldman Sachs Global Staples Forum
summary: NEW YORK, April 29, 2025--Colgate-Palmolive (NYSE:CL) President, Hill’s Pet Nutrition, John Hazlin, and Chief Investor Relations Officer and EVP, M&A, John Faucher, will participate in a fireside chat at the Goldman Sachs Global Staples Forum on Tuesday, May 13, 2025 at 8:15 am ET.
